Initialize git-hop repository structure with interactive setup for worktree conversion.

Usage:
  git-hop init [flags]

Aliases:
  init, setup, install

Flags:
      --dry-run          Show conversion steps without executing
      --enable-chdir     Install shell integration for automatic directory switching after hop commands
      --force            Skip clean repo check and backup requirements (DANGEROUS)
  -h, --help             help for init
      --keep-backup      Preserve backup after successful conversion
      --no-hooks         Skip automatic installation of .git-hop/hooks/ directory
      --regular          Use regular repo instead of bare
      --restore string   Restore repository from backup (manual rollback)

Global Flags:
      --config string   config file (default is $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/git-hop/config.json)
      --format string   Output format (table, json, yaml) (default "table")
  -g, --global          use global hopspace in $GIT_HOP_DATA_HOME (default: local)
      --json            output in JSON format
      --no-color        Disable ANSI colour
      --no-hints        Suppress next-step hints after command output
      --porcelain       machine-readable output
  -q, --quiet           Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose         verbose output
